---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Brackstone Digital" description="How Brackstone Digital collects, stores, and protects your personal data under UK GDPR.">
  <style is:global>
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: var(--color-brand-bg) !important; color: var(--color-brand-text) !important; font-family: var(--font-body) !important; overflow-x: hidden; }
    h1, h2, h3 { font-family: var(--font-heading) !important; }
    ::selection { background: var(--color-brand-primary); color: var(--color-brand-bg); }
  </style>

  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
        <span class="logo-mark">B</span>
        <span class="logo-text">Brackstone</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/#how">Process</a>
        <a href="/#capabilities">Services</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="nav-cta">Get in touch</a>
      </div>
      <button class="mobile-toggle" id="mobile-toggle" aria-label="Menu"><span></span><span></span></button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-glow"></div>
  </nav>
  <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobile-menu">
    <a href="/#how" class="mobile-link">Process</a>
    <a href="/#capabilities" class="mobile-link">Services</a>
    <a href="/contact" class="mobile-cta">Get in touch</a>
  </div>

  <main class="privacy-page">
    <div class="privacy-inner">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: 25 February 2026</p>

      <p>Brackstone Digital ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your personal data. This policy explains what data we collect, why we collect it, and your rights under the UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR) and the Data Protection Act 2018.</p>

      <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
      <p>Brackstone Digital is a B2B digital growth service based in Yorkshire, UK. For any data protection queries, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@brackstonedigital.co.uk">hello@brackstonedigital.co.uk</a>.</p>

      <h2>2. What data we collect</h2>
      <p>When you submit our contact form, we collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your full name</li>
        <li>Your email address</li>
        <li>Your message</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We may also collect technical data automatically, including your IP address, browser type, and pages visited, through cookies and analytics tools (see Section 6).</p>

      <h2>3. Why we collect it</h2>
      <p>We use your data for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>To respond to your enquiry</strong> — We use your name and email to reply to your message. Legal basis: legitimate interest in responding to your enquiry.</li>
        <li><strong>To follow up</strong> — We may send a small number of follow-up emails related to your enquiry. Legal basis: legitimate interest.</li>
        <li><strong>To improve our service</strong> — We use anonymous analytics to understand how visitors use our website. Legal basis: legitimate interest.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. How we store your data</h2>
      <p>Your data is stored securely on servers within the EEA/UK. We retain your personal data for no longer than 12 months from your last interaction with us, after which it is deleted. We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data.</p>

      <h2>5. Who we share it with</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share data with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email delivery services</strong> — To send follow-up communications</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics providers</strong> — To understand website usage (anonymised data)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>All third parties are bound by data processing agreements and comply with UK GDPR.</p>

      <h2>6. Cookies and tracking</h2>
      <p>We use:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Essential cookies</strong> — Required for the website to function</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — To understand visitor behaviour (anonymised)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</p>

      <h2>7. Your rights</h2>
      <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Access</strong> — Request a copy of the data we hold about you</li>
        <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — Ask us to correct inaccurate data</li>
        <li><strong>Erasure</strong> — Ask us to delete your data</li>
        <li><strong>Object</strong> — Object to our processing of your data</li>
        <li><strong>Portability</strong> — Request your data in a machine-readable format</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:hello@brackstonedigital.co.uk">hello@brackstonedigital.co.uk</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>

      <h2>8. Complaints</h2>
      <p>If you are unhappy with how we handle your data, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) at <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ico.org.uk</a>.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-glow-line"></div>
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-left">
        <a href="/" class="footer-logo">
          <span class="f-logo-mark">B</span>
          <span class="f-logo-text">Brackstone Digital</span>
        </a>
        <p class="footer-tagline">Full-stack growth for UK small businesses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-right">
        <div class="footer-col">
          <span class="footer-col-label">Services</span>
          <a href="/#capabilities">Outreach</a>
          <a href="/#capabilities">Voice AI</a>
          <a href="/#capabilities">Websites</a>
          <a href="/#capabilities">Paid Ads</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <span class="footer-col-label">Company</span>
          <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <span>&copy; 2026 Brackstone Digital. All rights reserved.</span>
    <span style="display:block;margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:0.72rem;opacity:0.55;line-height:1.5;">Brackstone Digital Limited, registered in England &amp; Wales, company no. 17159711. Registered office: 71-75 Shelton Street, Covent Garden, London, WC2H 9JQ.</span>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  @reference "../styles/global.css";

  /* Nav */
  .nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; padding: 0 2rem; background: rgba(15, 15, 26, 0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; }
  .nav-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 72px; }
  .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; }
  .logo-mark { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--color-brand-primary); color: var(--color-brand-bg); font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 70%, 70% 100%, 0 100%); }
  .logo-text { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--color-brand-text); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2.5rem; }
  .nav-links a { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-brand-muted); text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--color-brand-primary); }
  .nav-cta { padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem !important; background: var(--color-brand-primary) !important; color: var(--color-brand-bg) !important; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0.05em !important; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 70%, 85% 100%, 0 100%); }
  .nav-glow { position: absolute; bottom: -1px; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(191, 255, 0, 0.3), rgba(0, 212, 170, 0.2), transparent); }
  .mobile-toggle { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px; }
  .mobile-toggle span { display: block; width: 24px; height: 2px; background: var(--color-brand-primary); }
  .mobile-menu { display: none; position: fixed; top: 72px; left: 0; right: 0; background: rgba(15, 15, 26, 0.98); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); padding: 2rem; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; z-index: 99; }
  .mobile-menu.open { display: flex; }
  .mobile-link { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-brand-muted); text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
  .mobile-cta { display: inline-block; padding: 0.8rem 2rem; background: var(--color-brand-primary); color: var(--color-brand-bg); font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; font-size: 0.9rem; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 70%, 90% 100%, 0 100%); text-align: center; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .nav-links { display: none; } .mobile-toggle { display: flex; } .nav { padding: 0 1.25rem; } }

  /* Content */
  .privacy-page { padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem; }
  .privacy-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .privacy-inner h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-brand-text);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .updated {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-brand-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .privacy-inner h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-brand-primary);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .privacy-inner p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-brand-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .privacy-inner ul {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 1.5rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .privacy-inner li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-brand-muted);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .privacy-inner li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.65rem;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    background: var(--color-brand-primary);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .privacy-inner li strong { color: var(--color-brand-text); }

  .privacy-inner a {
    color: var(--color-brand-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .privacy-inner a:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) { .privacy-page { padding: 6rem 1.25rem 3rem; } }

  /* Footer */
  .footer { position: relative; background: var(--color-brand-bg); padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; }
  .footer-glow-line { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(191, 255, 0, 0.3), rgba(0, 212, 170, 0.2), transparent); }
  .footer-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 3rem; padding-bottom: 3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(191, 255, 0, 0.06); }
  .footer-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .f-logo-mark { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--color-brand-primary); color: var(--color-brand-bg); font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.85rem; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 70%, 70% 100%, 0 100%); }
  .f-logo-text { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-brand-text); }
  .footer-tagline { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-brand-muted); margin: 0; max-width: 280px; }
  .footer-right { display: flex; gap: 4rem; }
  .footer-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .footer-col-label { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--color-brand-primary); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; opacity: 0.6; }
  .footer-col a { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-brand-muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--color-brand-primary); }
  .footer-bottom { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 1.5rem; }
  .footer-bottom span { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-brand-muted); opacity: 0.5; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; } .footer-right { gap: 2.5rem; } .footer { padding: 3rem 1.25rem 1.5rem; } }
</style>

<script>
  const toggle = document.getElementById('mobile-toggle');
  const menu = document.getElementById('mobile-menu');
  toggle?.addEventListener('click', () => menu?.classList.toggle('open'));
  menu?.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(a => a.addEventListener('click', () => menu?.classList.remove('open')));
</script>
